Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TAG_ALARME As String Dim TAG_UAS As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") TAG_ALARME = Replace(Text28.Caption, "-", "_") TAG_UAS = Replace(Text31.Caption, "-", "_")
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "'"
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%' Or SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_ALARME & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String Dim TAG_ALARME As String Dim TAG_UAS As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_") TAG_ALARME = Replace(Text28.Caption, "-", "_") TAG_UAS = Replace(Text31.Caption, "-", "_")
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_ALARME & "' Or EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_UAS & "'"
' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer) On Error GoTo ErrHandler If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
